   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00096-B-000-00189"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168815">Wien XVIII.
                        Sternwartestrasse 71</rs></hi></addrLine></address><address><addrLine>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Gustav Schwarzkopf</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb51">Wien I</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb207301">Tiefer Graben 17</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00096-B-000-00190"/><salute>lieber Gu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tav,</salute> morgen nach dem <rs type="event" ref="#pmb88534" subtype="implied"><hi rend="latintype">Première</hi></rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind wir (da <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2173">Olga</rs> rauchige Locale noch
               vermeiden<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>oll) <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L04107-1"/>bei uns<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L04107-1"><ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1911-10-14" subtype="Cf"/>.
               </note>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb168815">Sternwarte<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>traße</rs>.
               Hoffentlich i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihnen <subst><del rend="overwritten">un</del><add place="inline">der</add></subst> Weg nicht zu weit u wir <c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehn Sie bei uns. Im Be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>itz des Billets <c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind Sie
               wohl.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr<lb/><signed>A.</signed></closer><postscript><dateline><date>13. X. 911</date></dateline></postscript></div>
      </body>
